trans-unit.source: Defines a point, associated with a user event, to be tracked in the potential execution path of a root workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: Definerer et punkt, som er forbundet med en bruker-hendelse, skal spores i potensielle kjøring av banen til en arbeidsflytforekomst som roten.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] An activity designer or a workflow designer may use the overloaded <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.TrackData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> and <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.TrackData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> methods to instrument the workflow to emit data to the runtime tracking infrastructure as a user event.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]En Aktivitetsdesigner eller designer arbeidsflyt kan bruke den overbelastet <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.TrackData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>og <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.TrackData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>metoder for å utstyre arbeidsflyten for å sende data til kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur som en bruker-hendelse.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.ActivityExecutionContext.TrackData%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.Activity.TrackData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The data emitted is referred to as user data.
trans-unit.target: Dataene slippes ut refereres til som brukerdata.

trans-unit.source: Unlike activity status events, and workflow status events, which occur only on status changes, user events can occur at any location that is instrumented in a workflow.
trans-unit.target: I motsetning til aktiviteten Statushendelser og arbeidsflyten Statushendelser, som bare forekommer på endres, kan det forekomme brukerhandlinger på hvor som helst som brukes i en arbeidsflyt.

trans-unit.source: There are many reasons to instrument a workflow to emit user events.
trans-unit.target: Det finnes mange grunner til utstyre en arbeidsflyt for å sende brukerhandlinger.

trans-unit.source: For example, a workflow designer may want to communicate logical state information about the progress of a workflow, or an activity designer might want to provide an opportunity to activity members at times other than an activity status change.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en arbeidsflyt utformer bør kommunisere logisk Tilstandsinformasjon om fremdriften for en arbeidsflyt, eller en Aktivitetsdesigner vil gir mulighet for å aktiviteten medlemmer noen ganger enn statusen aktiviteten endre.

trans-unit.source: A UserTrackPoint defines a point of interest in the potential execution path of a root workflow instance associated with a user event.
trans-unit.target: En UserTrackPoint definerer et punkt interessert i potensielt kjøring av banen til en arbeidsflytforekomst for roten knyttet til en bruker-hendelse.

trans-unit.source: A UserTrackPoint contains locations that are included in matching, locations that are excluded from matching, and any additional data that should be extracted from the workflow instance when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: En UserTrackPoint inneholder plasseringer som er inkludert i samsvarende, steder som er utelatt fra samsvarende og mer data som skal trekkes fra arbeidsflytforekomsten når spor punktet samsvarer.

trans-unit.source: You can add a UserTrackPoint to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile.UserTrackPoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName> to instruct the runtime tracking infrastructure to send a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> to the tracking service when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til en UserTrackPoint til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile.UserTrackPoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName>til be kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur for å sende en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>til Sporingstjenesten når spor punktet samsvarer.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingProfile.UserTrackPoints%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The user data is returned in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Brukerdataene returneres i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: A single UserTrackPoint may be matched at multiple points in the workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En enkelt UserTrackPoint kan samsvare på flere steder i arbeidsflytforekomsten.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> contains match conditions for a location associated with a user event in the potential execution path of a workflow instance.
trans-unit.target: En <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>inneholder samsvarer betingelser for en plassering som er knyttet til en bruker hendelse i potensielt kjøring av banen til en arbeidsflytforekomst.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: You can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> to define locations that should be included in matching for the track point.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>objekter til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>til å definere plasseringer som skal inkluderes i samsvarende for spor punktet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: Similarly, you can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> to define locations that should be excluded from matching for the track point.
trans-unit.target: På samme måte kan du legge til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>objekter til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>til å definere plasseringer som skal utelates fra samsvarende for spor punktet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: You can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A> to specify data that should be extracted from the workflow instance when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>objekter og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objekter til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A>til å angi dataene som skal trekkes fra arbeidsflytforekomsten når spor punktet samsvarer.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: The extracted data will be returned in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Utpakkede dataene vil bli returnert i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: You can add to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A> to specify additional information associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>til å angi tilleggsinformasjon som er knyttet til spor punktet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>

trans-unit.source: These annotations will be returned in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Disse merknader vil bli returnert i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: For an example of how to use this class, see the [Tracking Using User Track Points Sample](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d894a18a-a4c6-467e-9a42-8be025ecd4d5).
trans-unit.target: Et eksempel på hvordan du bruker denne klassen, kan du se den [sporing ved hjelp av brukeren spor punkt utvalg](http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/d894a18a-a4c6-467e-9a42-8be025ecd4d5).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes an empty track point.
trans-unit.target: Standardkonstruktøren initialiserer et tomt Sporingspunkt.

trans-unit.source: No matching locations, excluded locations, data extracts or annotations are specified.
trans-unit.target: Ingen samsvarende plasseringer, utelatte plasseringer, trekker ut data eller kommentarer er angitt.

trans-unit.source: You must configure the track point by adding at least one <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du må konfigurere spor punktet ved å legge til minst én <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: You may optionally add the appropriate objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til de aktuelle objektene som eventuelt <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A>, og <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Annotations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.Extracts%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of annotations associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen av merknader som er knyttet til spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: You can add to Annotations to specify annotations to be returned in Annotations when the track point is matched.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til merknader for å angi merknader som skal returneres i merknader når spor punktet samsvarer.

trans-unit.source: If Annotations is empty, no annotations are associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Hvis merknader er tom, er noen merknader tilknyttet spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: Annotations are `strings` that you define that contain information associated with the track point.
trans-unit.target: Kommentarer er `strings` du definerer som inneholder informasjon som er knyttet til spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: For example, an annotation could contain information about the possible execution path the workflow can take from this track point, or it could contain information to be displayed in a user interface.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en merknad kan inneholde informasjon om mulige kjøring-banen arbeidsflyten kan ta fra spor nå, eller den kan inneholde informasjonen som skal vises i et brukergrensesnitt.

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingAnnotationCollection"></xref>.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of locations that should be excluded from the track point by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Henter til steder som skal utelates fra spor punktet av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur-samlingen.

trans-unit.source: If any of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objects in ExcludedLocations is matched for a particular user event, the track point will not be matched and no <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> will be sent to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Hvis noen av de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>objekter i ExcludedLocations sammenlignet for en bestemt bruker-hendelse, vil ikke samsvarer med spor-punktet, og ingen <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>sendes til Sporingstjenesten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: If ExcludedLocations is empty, there are no excluded locations.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ExcludedLocations er tom, finnes det ingen utelatte plasseringer.

trans-unit.source: You can use ExcludedLocations to exclude specific locations from being tracked by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Du kan bruke ExcludedLocations for å utelate bestemte steder fra spores av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: For example, you can exclude a subset of locations that are specified in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A> in order to more precisely refine the locations that should be tracked by the track point.
trans-unit.target: Du kan for eksempel utelate et delsett av plasseringer som er angitt i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>for å forbedre tekstskriften plasseringene som skal spores av Spor punktet.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.MatchingLocations%2A>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection"></xref> that specifies locations to be excluded from the track point.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection"> </xref> som angir plasseringer som skal utelates fra spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: Gets a collection that specifies data to be extracted from the workflow instance and sent to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Henter en samling som angir dataene som er hentet fra arbeidsflytforekomsten og sendes til Sporingstjenesten.

trans-unit.source: When the track point is matched, the runtime tracking infrastructure sends a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord> to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: Når Spor punktet samsvarer, kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur sender en <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>til Sporingstjenesten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: The user data is returned in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Brukerdataene returneres i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.UserData%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The runtime tracking infrastructure can also extract data specified in Extracts from the workflow instance and send this in the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.
trans-unit.target: Kjøring sporing infrastruktur kan trekke ut data som er angitt i arbeidsflytforekomsten, trekker ut og sende dette i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord>

trans-unit.source: The extracted data is encapsulated in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem> records and returned in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: Datatypen utpakkede innkapslet i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>poster og returnerte i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingRecord.Body%2A?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem>

trans-unit.source: You can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract> objects to Extracts to specify member data that should be extracted from the activity associated with the user event and you can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> objects to Extracts to specify member data that should be extracted from the root activity of the workflow.
trans-unit.target: Du kan legge til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>objektene trekker ut til å angi medlemsdata som skal trekkes fra aktiviteten tilknyttet bruker hendelsen, og du kan legge til <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract>objektene trekker ut til å angi medlemsdata som skal trekkes fra den primære aktiviteten av arbeidsflyten.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract>

trans-unit.source: An <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ExtractCollection"></xref> that specifies data to be extracted and sent to the tracking service.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ExtractCollection"> </xref> som angir data som skal trekkes ut og sendt til Sporingstjenesten.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: Gets the collection of locations that should be included in matching for the track point by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Henter samlingen til steder som skal inkluderes i samsvarende for punktet spor av kjøretiden sporing infrastrukturen.

trans-unit.source: If MatchingLocations is empty, the track point cannot be matched by the runtime tracking infrastructure.
trans-unit.target: Hvis MatchingLocations er tom, samsvarer ikke spor punktet av kjøretiden sporing infrastruktur.

trans-unit.source: You must add at least one <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> to MatchingLocations for the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> to participate in matching.
trans-unit.target: Du må legge til minst én <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>til MatchingLocations for den <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint>delta i samsvarende.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: The track point will be matched if any of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objects in MatchingLocations is matched and none of the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> objects in <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> is matched.
trans-unit.target: Spor punktet samsvare Hvis noen av de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>objekter i MatchingLocations sammenlignet og ingen av <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>objekter i <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A>samsvarer.</xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackPoint.ExcludedLocations%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation> </xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocation>

trans-unit.source: A <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection"></xref> that specifies the locations to be matched for the track point.
trans-unit.target: En <xref href="System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.UserTrackingLocationCollection"> </xref> som angir plasseringen til å samsvare for spor punktet.

trans-unit.source: The default is an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Standarden er en tom samling.
